results.title: Samsung Galaxy S3, S4, Eye and Wallet Dock - Valet
results.description:
This dock/valet was designed to accept Galaxy S3 and S4 smartphones with a thin style case. This dock feature a convenient place to store eyeglasses or sun glasses. Wallets can be stowed away securely in a slot to the side of the dock. There is also plenty of storage at the rear of the dock for pocket items. This dock will also accept plenty of other android phones that are bottom center charging and of a similar dimension as the GX3 or GX4 phones.    

The details:

Easy access to most buttons and phone removal

Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock/valet.

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets.

Item ships USPS priority 2 to 3 day mail

This docking station has will come with a natural sanded smooth finish 

Aprx. 7 inches tall x 9.5 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 9.5 inches.

Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz

results.title: Universal Smart Eye and Watch Dock Valet
results.description:
The Universal Eye and watch dock is minimalistic and a feature rich solution to both charge and display your phone no matter if it charges off center or on the side. Perfect to use with an alarm clock app on a nightstand. This Dock/valet has an integrated slot that can keep 1 to 2 watches at the ready. A carved pocket in the base can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, or other items you may carry in your daily life. A slot to the side can securely store a wallet. Additional storage can be found in the rear of the dock for keys or change etc. 


The details: 

Dock will accept nearly any phone 

Slot provided for 1 to 2 watches, depending on size

Front pocket can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, pens etc.

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets. 

Can be used with or without a case 

This docking station has been sanded smooth and finished with boiled linseed oil.

Aprx. 5.5 inches tall x 13 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 13 inches.  

Made out of red Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz

PLEASE NOTE: On hand stock quantities will vary. If this is for a gift and should ship out before 2 weeks after purchase, please send me a convo.

This Dock/valet has an integrated slot that can keep 3 to 4 watches at the ready. A carved pocket in the base can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, or other items you may carry in your daily life. A slot to the side can securely store a wallet or check book. Additional storage can be found in the rear of the dock for keys or change etc. 


The details: 


Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock/valet. 

Slot provided for 3 to 4 watches, depending on size

Front pocket can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, pens etc.

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets. 

Item ships USPS priority 1 to 3 day mail

This is meant to be used with a Samsung Galaxy S5, S4, or S3 with no case or a very slim case. 

This docking station is sanded smooth and finished with boiled linseed oil.

Aprx. 7 inches tall x 10 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 10 inches.  

Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz

PLEASE NOTE: On hand stock quantities will vary. If this is for a gift and should ship out before 2 weeks after purchase, please send me a convo.

results.title: Samsung Galaxy S3, S4, S5, 6 Eye and Wallet Dock - Valet
results.description:
This dock/valet was designed to accept Galaxy S3, S4, and S5 smartphones with a thin style case. This dock feature a convenient place to store eyeglasses or sun glasses. Wallets can be stowed away securely in a slot to the side of the dock. There is also plenty of storage at the rear of the dock for pocket items. This dock will also accept plenty of other android phones that are bottom center charging and of a similar dimension as the GX3 or GX4 phones.    

The details:

Easy access to most buttons and phone removal

Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock/valet.

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets.

Item ships USPS priority 2 to 3 day mail

This docking station has been sanded smooth and finished in boiled linseed oil 

Aprx. 7 inches tall x 9.5 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 9.5 inches.

Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz
